===Etymology===
From {{etyl|ang}} ''[[wiht]]'', ''ġewiht'', from {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{recons|wihtiz|lang=gem-pro}}, {{recons|wekhtiz|(ga)wekhtiz|lang=gem-pro}} (cf. {{recons|weganą|lang=gem-pro}}). Compare Dutch {{term|gewicht|lang=nl}}, German {{term|Gewicht|lang=de}}.

